&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;However &lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;bold and italic&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; doesn&amp;rsquo;t play well when used together like in markdown.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;However &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;bold and italic&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt; doesn&amp;rsquo;t play well when used together like in markdown.&lt;/li&gt;
